`Memory Usage` might be better metric name

It is better to specify base port. By default it starts from `8000` and we don't want to use a common port here. So lets set `basePort` (https://www.npmjs.com/package/portfinder#ports-search-scope) to a number something like `10000`
`Random port is:` => `Workflow telemetry server port is:`
